      "content": "but what's the point of just \"taking a breath\" when every breath just reminds me of what i lost? it doesn't feel like i'm being strong, it just feels like i'm being forced to endure a life that i don't even want anymore. everything is just so heavy and i'm so tired of fighting it.",
